<br>
I am definitely a casual player.  I played EQ for three years and only got up to 33rd level.  I started about 8 mos after EQ went live, so I guess you could call me an &quot;old school&quot; monk.  I remember going down to Innothul Swamp (sp?) to get my mesh gloves since they were magic and would let me solo wisps! I remember camping for ages to get my Treant Fists, only to have Gem Inlaid Gauntlets show up a few months later.  I remember Kuark coming out and being envious of the lizzies and pissed off at  all of the new monk weapons (monk weapons?!!? what do we need those for? we have our fists and feet!!!).  I remember one of the reasons I picked monk was because they were self-reliant and I wouldn't have to worry about loot or twinks...<br>
<br>
Well, Verant changed the class that I originally started to play to such an extent that I really had no desire to play it anymore.<br>
<br>
Since switching to DAoC I've been much happier.  The game is MUCH friendlier to the casual player.  I can get on and find a group pretty quickly and if I don't I can still solo (and if you try and tell me that EQ Monks can solo, my answer is yes they can if they are twinked out, I didn't have that luxury...).<br>
<br>
I play for about 6 hours a week, sometime a bit more, sometimes less.  DAoC makes this a fairly pleasant experience.<br>
<br>
I can see how hard-core players would become bored with DAoC fairly quick, but for me it's quite the improvement. <p><img src = "http://www.criminy.net/images/eqsig.jpg" width="432" height="72" align="center"> <br> <align="left"><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="1"><b>Monk of the 33rd Sash - - - My feet hurt... <i>with Destiny!</i></b></font>  </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub38.ezboard.com/uliktha.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Liktha</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(4/18/02 12:16:54 pm)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.myoswego.net/~stacisplace/stacipersonalpic.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Poll:    How has DAoC affected EQ for you??</span><hr size=1> Heh..hadn't checked this since I posted.<br>
